<div id="post-1309" class="cf post-1309 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2006/02/advice-for-lucent/" title="Advice for Lucent" rel="bookmark">Advice for Lucent</a>
		
	</h2>

	
	
	<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
	
		<div class="post-date">		
			<p class="post-month">Feb</p>
			<p class="post-day">24</p>
			<p class="post-year">2006</p>				
		</div>

		Yesterday, I helped judge the Wharton business case competition. This is a program put on by the Wharton Technology Club, in which MBA students analyze a business problem presented by a real company. This year&#8217;s sponsor was Lucent, which asked the students to recommend a strategic initiative for the company. Several Lucent executives also served as judges.
		
	</div>

