</div>

<div id="post-1305" class="cf post-1305 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-uncategorized">

	<h2>
		<span class="post-format"></span>
		<a href="http://werblog.com/2006/02/reminder-supernova-party-on-thursday/" title="Reminder &#8212; Supernova party on Thursday!" rel="bookmark">Reminder &#8212; Supernova party on Thursday!</a>
		
