			<p class="post-month">Feb</p>
			<p class="post-day">14</p>
			<p class="post-year">2006</p>				
		</div>

		This Thursday night, I&#8217;m hosting a pre-pre-Supernova party in San Francisco. Come hang out and network with a collection of technology innovators, entrepreneurs, investors, thinkers, and others. It will be at Cha-Am Thai, near the Moscone Center in San Francisco. Full details and RSVP information are at: http://www.socialtext.net/snparty Feel free to invite friends. However, we do have a cap on space. So if you&#8217;d like to come, please be sure ...
		
